<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="295" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,705,804]" pageId="1" pageNumber="295">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,741,767]" pageId="1" pageNumber="295">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is a combination of the first syllable of the family name of Roger-Paul Dechambre and his original genus name that recognised Beck. The name is masculine in gender.
</paragraph>
